-- Sarkozy Hopes to Sign Mirage Accord on December India Visit, Tribune Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-09-28T04:24:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/sarkozy-hopes-to-sign-mirage-accord-on-december-india-visit-tribune-says.html
French President Nicolas Sarkozy
will visit India from Dec. 4 to Dec. 7, daily La Tribune
reported, citing unidentified people.  Sarkozy hopes to sign a contract worth 1.5 billion euros
for Dassault Aviation SA and Thales SA to upgrade 51 Mirage
combat jets on the trip, the newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  